      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. While it shows a few minor signs of careful previous use, it remains clean, attractive, and ready for its next adventure. It's a solid, high-quality choice for anyone looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road!",
