    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for a new owner who prioritizes utility over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches and the clear coat is starting to fade on the roof, while the interior shows some wear on the driver's seat and carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that provides reliable transportation for anyone looking for a budget-friendly option.",
