    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for parts or as a major project for someone with mechanical expertise. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy oxidation on the paint, several large dents on the passenger side, and visible rust bubbling through the wheel arches. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and requires immediate attention, the transmission shifts harshly, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn with some missing trim pieces. It is being sold strictly 'as-is,' so we encourage interested buyers to inspect it thoroughly before purchase.",
